\c 8
\s Mazita eVaJudha vakanosvika kuJerusarema naEzira
\p
\v 1 Zvino ava ndivo misoro yemadzibaba avo, uye dzinza reavo vakakwira neni kubva kuBhabhironi, pakutonga kwaAritakiserikisi mambo.
\v 2 Pavanakomana vaPinehasi, Gerishomu\x + 1 Makor. 24.3,4.\x*; pavanakomana vaItamari\x + 1 Makor. 24.3,4.\x*, Dhaniyeri\x + Neh. 10.6.\x*; pavanakomana vaDhavhidhi, Hatushi\x + 1 Makor. 3.22. Neh. 10.4. 12.2.\x*.
\v 3 Pavanakomana vaShekaniya\x + 1 Makor. 3.21.\x*, pavanakomana vaParoshi\x + 2.3.\x*, Zekariya; uye pamwe naye kwakaverengwa nemadzinza evanhurume, zana nemakumi mashanu.
\v 4 Pavanakomana vaPahati-Moabhi, Eriowenai mwanakomana waZerahiya; uye pamwe naye vanhurume mazana maviri\x + 2.6.\x*.
\v 5 Pavanakomana vaShekaniya, mwanakomana waJahazieri; uye pamwe naye vanhurume mazana matatu\x + 1 Makor. 3.21.\x*.
\v 6 Uye pavanakomana vaAdhini, Ebhedhi mwanakomana waJonatani; uye pamwe naye vanhurume makumi mashanu\x + 2.15.\x*.
\v 7 Nepavanakomana vaErami, Jeshaya mwanakomana waAtariya; uye pamwe naye vanhurume makumi manomwe\x + 2.7.\x*.
\v 8 Uye pavanakomana vaShefatiya, Zebhadhiya mwanakomana waMikayeri; uye pamwe naye vanhurume makumi masere\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 9 Pavanakomana vaJoabhi, Obhadhiya mwanakomana waJehieri; uye pamwe naye vanhurume mazana maviri negumi nevasere\x + 2.6.\x*.
\v 10 Nepavanakomana vaSheromiti, mwanakomana waJosifiya; uye pamwe naye vanhurume zana nemakumi matanhatu.
\v 11 Nepavanakomana vaBhebhayi, Zekariya mwanakomana waBhebhayi; uye pamwe naye vanhurume makumi maviri nevasere\x + 2.11,12. 10.28. Neh. 10.15.\x*.
\v 12 Nepavanakomana vaAzagadhi, Johwanani mwanakomana waHakatani; uye pamwe naye vanhurume zana negumi\x + 2.11,12. 10.28. Neh. 10.15.\x*.
\v 13 Nepavanakomana vekupedzisira vaAdhonikami, avo mazita avo ari awa: Erifereti, Jeieri, naShemaya; uye pamwe navo vanhurume makumi matanhatu\x + 2.13.\x*.
\v 14 Uye pavanakomana vaBhigivhai, Utai naZabhudhi; uye pamwe navo vanhurume makumi manomwe\x + 2.2,14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Zvino ndakavaunganidza parwizi rwunoenda kuAhavha\x + 8.21,31.\x*; tikadzika musasapo mazuva matatu; ndokucherekedza vanhu nevapristi, uye handina kuwanapo wevanakomana VaRevhi\x + 7.7.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino ndakatuma \add nhume\add* kuna Eriezeri, kuna Arieri, kuna Shemaya, nekuna Erinatani, nekuna Jaribhati, nekuna Erinatani, nekuna Natani, nekuna Zekariya\x + 8.3,11. Neh. 8.4. 12.41.\x*, nekuna Meshurami, misoro, nekuna Joyaribhi, nekuna Erinatani, vainzwisisa\x + 10.15. Neh. 3.4,30. 6.18. 8.4. 10.7,20. 12.33.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino ndakavatuma kuna Idho musoro panzvimbo Kasifiya; ndokuisa mumuromo mavo mashoko ekutaura kuna Idho, \add ne\add*hama dzake VaNetinimi, panzvimbo Kasifiya, kuti vauye kwatiri nevashumiri veimba yaMwari wedu.
\v 18 Zvino zvichienderana neruoko rwakanaka rwaMwari wedu pamusoro pedu, vakativigira munhu anonzwisisa\x + 7.6.\x*, wevanakomana vaMahiri, mwanakomana waRevhi, mwanakomana waIsraeri\x + 1 Makor. 6.19.\x*; naSherebhiya, nevanakomana vake nehama dzake, gumi nevasere\x + 8.24. Neh. 8.7. 9.4,5. 10.12. 12.24. Neh. 12.8.\x*;
\v 19 naHashabhiya\x + 8.24. Neh. 3.17. 10.11. 12.24.\x*, uye pamwe naye Jeshaya wevanakomana vaMerari, hama dzake nevanakomana vavo, makumi maviri\x + 1 Makor. 6.1,16.\x*;
\v 20 paVaNetinimiwo\x + 7.7. 1 Makor. 9.2.\x*, Dhavhidhi nemachinda vavaiva vapa pabasa reVaRevhi, VaNetinimi mazana maviri nemakumi maviri; vese vakarehwa nemazita\x + Num.. 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Zvino ndakadanidzirapo mutsanyo\x + 2 Makor. 20.3.\x* parwizi rweAhavha\x + 8.21,31.\x*, kuti tizvirwadzise pamberi paMwari wedu\x + Rev. 16.29.\x*, kutsvaka kwaari nzira yakatiruramira isu nevanana vedu nefuma yedu yose\x + Map. 5.8.\x*.
\v 22 Nokuti ndakanyara kukumbira kuna mambo boka revarwi nevatasvi vemabhiza kutibatsira kurwisa vavengi panzira; nokuti taiva tataura namambo, tichiti: Ruoko rwaMwari wedu rwuri pamusoro pevese\x + 7.6.\x* vanomutsvaka kuti zvivanakire\x + VaRom. 8.28.\x*; asi simba rake nehasha dzake zviri pamusoro pevese vanomusiya\x + Josh. 24.20. 2 Makor. 15.2.\x*.
\v 23 Naizvozvo takatsanya, ndokutsvaka kuna Mwari wedu pamusoro paizvozvi; zvino akanyengetedzeka nesu\x + Gen.. 25.21. Isa. 19.22.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Zvino ndakatsaura gumi nevaviri pamisoro yevapristi, vaiti: Sherebhia\x + 8.18.\x*, Hashabhiya, uye gumi vehama dzavo pamwe navo\x + 8.19.\x*;
\v 25 ndokuvayerera sirivha, negoridhe, nemidziyo\x + 7.15,16.\x*, chipo cheimba yaMwari wedu\x + Eki. 25.2.\x*, mambo nemakurukota ake nemachinda ake naIsraeri wose waivapo chavaiva vapa\x + Vato. 20.48.\x*.
\v 26 Ndakayererawo muruoko rwavo matarenda mazana matanhatu nemakumi mashanu esirivha, nematarenda zana emidziyo yesirivha, \add ne\add*matarenda zana egoridhe;
\v 27 nembiya makumi maviri dzegoridhe\x + 1.10.\x* rakasvika madhariki churu; nemidziyo miviri yendarira yakanaka inopenya yaishuviwa segoridhe\x + 1 Makor. 29.7.\x*.
\v 28 Zvino ndakati kwavari: Imwi muri vatsvene kuna Jehovha\x + Rev. 21.6.\x*, nemidziyo mitsvene\x + Rev. 22.2,3.\x*, uye sirivha negoridhe, chipo chekuzvidira kuna Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba enyu\x + 7.15,16.\x*.
\v 29 Mu\add zvi\add*rindire, uye muchengetedze, kusvika mazviyera pamberi pemisoro yevapristi neVaRevhi, nemisoro yemadzibaba aIsraeri paJerusarema, \add mu\add*makamuri eimba yaJehovha\x + 10.6. 2 Madz. 23.11.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino vapristi neVaRevhi vakagamuchira chiyero chesirivha nechegoridhe nechemidziyo, kuti vazviise paJerusarema paimba yaMwari wedu.
\p
\v 31 Zvino takabva parwizi rweAhavha\x + 8.15,21.\x* neregumi nemaviri remwedzi wekutanga kuenda kuJerusarema\x + 7.9.\x*; uye ruoko rwaMwari wedu rwaiva pamusoro pedu, akatinunura paruoko rwemuvengi nemuvandiri panzira\x + 7.6.\x*.
\v 32 Zvino takasvika paJerusarema, ndokugarapo mazuva matatu\x + Neh. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Zvino pazuva rechina sirivha negoridhe nemidziyo zvakayerwa muimba yaMwari wedu\x + 8.26,30.\x* neruoko rwaMeremoti\x + Neh. 3.4,21. 10.5.\x* mwanakomana wemupristi Uriya\x + Neh. 3.4,21. 8.4.\x*; uye pamwe naye Eriazari mwanakomana waPinehasi, uye pamwe navo Jozabhadhi mwanakomana waJeshuwa\x + 10.23. Neh. 8.7. 11.16.\x*, naNowadhiya mwanakomana waBhinui, VaRevhi\x + 2.10. Neh. 3.24. 10.9.\x*,
\v 34 pauwandu \add uye\add* pauremu hwezvose; uye uremu hwese hwakanyorwa panguva iyoyo.
\v 35 Vana veutapwa vaiva vadzoka pautapwa vakapa zvipo zvinopiswa kuna Mwari waIsraeri\x + 2.1.\x*, nzombe diki gumi nembiri dzaIsraeri wese, makondohwe makumi mapfumbamwe nematanhatu, makwayana makumi manomwe nemanomwe, nhongo gumi nembiri dzembudzi, chipo chechivi; zvese chiri chipo chinopiswa kuna Jehovha\x + 6.17. 2 Makor. 29.21.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Zvino vakapa mirairo yamambo\x + 7.21.\x* kumachinda amambo\x + Esi. 3.12. 8.9. 9.3. Dhan. 3.2,3,27. 6.2, 3.\x* nevatongi\x + 1 Madz. 10.15. Neh. 2.7,9. 3.7.\x* mhiri kwerwizi, ivo ndokutsigira vanhu neimba yaMwari\x + 1.4.\x*.